#

Sweet and Spicy Mango Glazed Chicken

$15.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

ChickenGluten-FreeDinnerEasy

Description

A vibrant dish featuring succulent chicken glazed with a sweet and spicy mango sauce, served with a side of cilantro-lime rice and fresh vegetables.

Ingredients

  • Chicken Breast: 2 pieces
  • Mango Puree: 1/2 cup
  • Honey: 2 tablespoons
  • Soy Sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic Cloves: 2, minced
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Lime Juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
